    11 ) lsipc;read cc ;; # ]--╼▰ [ Show Information on IPC Facilities Currently Employed in the System ]
    12 ) lstopo;read cc ;; # ]--╼▰ lstopo-no-graphics, hwloc-ls - Show the topology of the system
